<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It is not possible to check if a field of a QueryHit is empty with the empty() function.</p>

<p>e.g.:
When i have a field "content", i would access this by calling:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$hit-&gt;content;
</code></pre>

<p>It is not possible to check, if the field is empty with:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (empty($hit-&gt;content))  {...}
</code></pre>

<p>empty($hit-&gt;content) is always {{true}}. I think this is because the {{__isset}} method is not implemented in the QueryHit object and {{isset}} is the first check that is done by {{empty}}</p>

